description.narrative: The overall project idea of low-emission development (LED) is to address climate change in Croatia by shifting towards low-carbon development that offers substantial opportunities and ensures continued high growth and sustainable development, based on the Low Emission Development Strategy (hereafter LEDS). LEDS aims at reducing greenhouse gas emissions, environmental protection, stimulating economic growth through sustainability, creating opportunities for new jobs and guiding society towards long-term sustainable development.
